FS: 1889 E.R. Williams Game cards, all PSA graded.  These are among the higher graded examples in the population report.  VCP does not show a lot of sales of the game cards, unlike the cards depicting contemporary players, which are pretty unique and interesting.  All prices are Paypal, net to me.  Shipping is $3.70 for one card, $4.70 for two, and free for 3 or more.  PM me.  Sorry for the horizontal photos (don't know how to correct that!!).  Thanks!!!!!!
